sequenceDiagram
    participant CI as CI/CD Pipeline<br/>(Konflux / GitHub Actions)
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>Go CLI
    participant HF_Col as HuggingFace API<br/>Collections Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF_Model as HuggingFace API<br/>Models Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF_README as HuggingFace<br/>README Files<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as registry.redhat.io<br/>OCI Distribution API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant Container as Runtime Container<br/>UBI9-micro<br/>UID 1001
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>Volume Mount

    Note over CI,Dashboard: Flow 1: Build-Time Model Catalog Generation

    CI->>Extractor: Trigger pipeline execution

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Extractor,HF_Col: Step 1: Discover Model Collections
        Extractor->>HF_Col: GET /api/users/RedHatAI/collections<br/>Auth: None (public)
        HF_Col-->>Extractor: Collection list (slugs)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Extractor,HF_Col: Step 2: Fetch Collection Details
        Extractor->>HF_Col: GET /api/collections/{slug}<br/>Auth: None (public)
        HF_Col-->>Extractor: Collection items (model references)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Extractor,Registry: Step 3: Extract ModelCar Metadata
        Extractor->>Registry: GET OCI manifest + layers<br/>Auth: Docker credentials
        Registry-->>Extractor: Model card markdown from OCI layers
    end

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Extractor,HF_Model: Step 4: Enrich with HuggingFace Details
        Extractor->>HF_Model: GET /api/models/{id}<br/>Auth: None (public)
        HF_Model-->>Extractor: Model details (tags, license, etc.)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Extractor,HF_README: Step 5: Fetch README Content
        Extractor->>HF_README: GET /{model}/raw/main/README.md<br/>Auth: None (public)
        HF_README-->>Extractor: README markdown with YAML frontmatter
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Extractor,FS: Step 6-7: Generate Catalog Files
        Extractor->>FS: Write output/*/models/metadata.yaml<br/>(per-model metadata)
        Extractor->>FS: Write data/models-catalog.yaml<br/>(aggregated catalog)
    end

    Note over CI,Dashboard: Flow 2: Runtime Catalog Consumption

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Container,Dashboard: Catalog Data Serving
        CI->>Container: Build container image<br/>(copy catalog into UBI9-micro)
        Dashboard->>Container: Volume mount or docker cp
        Container-->>Dashboard: /app/data/models-catalog.yaml<br/>(static file read)
    end
